Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand our policies and practices for collecting, processing, using, retaining, disclosing, and storing your information. By agreeing to our privacy policy in the Services, or to cookies on our Website, you confirm that you understand, accept, and consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
The capitalized terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meaning as those used in Wavve’s Terms and Conditions, unless expressly noted otherwise.
